vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments regarding a proposal to consider the Ceremonial Street Name request for “Sr. Cpl. A. Pargas #8001” as a street topper on Goldman Street between Dennison Street and Bickers Street and an ordinance granting the street topper - Financing: New street blades to be prepared and paid for by the City of Dallas (see Fiscal Information for potential future costs)
